---
title: Fully Loaded Falafel Wrap with Hummus Dressing and Tabbouleh
description: This classic wrap just got a plant-based makeover and it's better than ever! Flavour-packed falafel is covered in a delightfully bright and creamy hummus dressing, paired with a fresh tabbouleh, for a perfect weeknight meal.
